languages.text: "Возможно, Неумирающий не забрал его вовремя, и он занимает не свое место. Мы скоро узнаем".
languages.translation_comment: Abelard: "A disorganised rabble should not be capable of bringing down a world like Rykad Minoris. Is the governor exerting every effort to restore order here? I am not convinced."

languages.text: "Perhaps the Undying One did not claim him at the right time, and now he occupies a place that is not his. We will soon find out."
languages.original_text: "Возможно, Неумирающий не забрал его вовремя, и он занимает не свое место. Мы скоро узнаем".

languages.text: "Vielleicht hat der Todlose ihn nicht zur richtigen Zeit geholt, und nun belegt er einen Plan, der nicht der seine ist. Wir werden es bald herausfinden."
languages.original_text: "Perhaps the Undying One did not claim him at the right time, and now he occupies a place that is not his. We will soon find out."

traits.locale_text: "Vielleicht hat der Todlose ihn nicht zur richtigen Zeit geholt, und nun belegt er einen Plan, der nicht der seine ist. Wir werden es bald herausfinden."

languages.text: « Peut-être l'Immortel a-t-il trop tardé à le rappeler à Lui et occupe-t-il à présent une place qui n'est pas la sienne. Nous n'allons pas tarder à être fixés. »
languages.original_text: "Perhaps the Undying One did not claim him at the right time, and now he occupies a place that is not his. We will soon find out."

languages.text: «Tal vez el Inmortal no se lo llevó en el momento adecuado y ahora ocupa un lugar que no le corresponde. Pronto lo descubriremos».
languages.original_text: "Perhaps the Undying One did not claim him at the right time, and now he occupies a place that is not his. We will soon find out."

traits.locale_text: «Tal vez el Inmortal no se lo llevó en el momento adecuado y ahora ocupa un lugar que no le corresponde. Pronto lo descubriremos».

languages.text: 「おそらく、不死の者が適切な時期に彼を引き取らなかった。そして、今や彼のものではない場所を占領している。きっとすぐに分かるだろう」
languages.original_text: "Perhaps the Undying One did not claim him at the right time, and now he occupies a place that is not his. We will soon find out."

traits.locale_text: 「おそらく、不死の者が適切な時期に彼を引き取らなかった。そして、今や彼のものではない場所を占領している。きっとすぐに分かるだろう」

languages.text: “或许不死之神并没有在合适的时候把他带走，而他现在占据了不属于他的地方。我们很快就会明白是怎么回事了。”
languages.original_text: "Perhaps the Undying One did not claim him at the right time, and now he occupies a place that is not his. We will soon find out."

languages.text: "Belki de Ölmeyen, onu doğru vakitte yanına almamıştır. O da şimdi kendine ait olmayan bir yere tutunmuştur. Yakında öğreneceğiz."
languages.original_text: "Perhaps the Undying One did not claim him at the right time, and now he occupies a place that is not his. We will soon find out."
